      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the reply. i'm already drinking a lot of water like u said, maybe like 3 or 4 liters a day now. do u think if i just keep the water intake high it'll help the shakiness go away? i really dont want to go to the clinic if it's just something i can fix at home with hydration.",
